--> Before doing this project you have to check whether the library langdetect " Language Detector " is installed or not .
To check here are some commands can check through Command lines, jupyter notebook.

  Through Command Lines in Windows: 

    python -m pip show numpy

  Through Jupyter Notebook:

    conda list langdetect

If Langdetect is Not Installed

Steps to Install Langdetect through Command Line:
  pip install langdetect
  
  and Click Enter.

Library is installed 
  
-->

# Source Code

from langdetect import detect
t=input("Enter any text in any language: ")
print(detect(t))
